  "texts": [
    "In this work, we identify the MRS spectra affected by the moon light by the condition of moon flg = 1 or lunardate = 14, 15, or 16.",
    "The MRS spectra that meet this condition are removed from our sample.",
    "To minimize the influence of the rotational broadening effect on the Hα line profile, the MRS spectra with large projected rotational velocity (v sin i) should be avoided.",
    "The LAMOST MRS Parameter Catalog provides the v sin i values (vsini lasp parameter in the catalog) for the MRS spectra with v sin i > 30 km/s.",
    "For the spectra with v sin i less than 30 km/s, vsini lasp parameter is not available and is set to -9999.0 in the catalog."
  ],
